    * Sword for Hire
    * Trollstone Caverns
    * Weirdworld

@{b}Microdot@{ub} (Windows)

This is a conversion of the 1975 PB board game "Microdot", for up to 4
players. Players can be controlled by human or IBM PC. Visual C 6.0
source code is included.

The object of Microdot is to capture a Diplomatic Bag from any enemy
territory to your own and bring it back safely to your own HQ square.
The first player to succeed in this mission wins the game.
@endnode

